The structure of the code for the messages will be as follows

EVENT ID

XXYY

X -> Will be the number that should receive the message
Y -> Will be the code of wich message should be sent

This is the list of possilbe messages, the text sent in each case can be changed via "interface"

01	Power interrupted
02	Battery in error

11	Card balance too low
12	Unknown SMS's received

20	Received command not valid
21	ACK Received
22	NACK Received

30	New command password is ****

A file in the system will have the message text stored in a folder the file name is the same as the message code

A file in the system will have the phone number stored the number will be the same as X code on the event ID


